data.description: Move in ready 1.5 story.  Remodeled kitchen with new soft close cabinets and granite countertops has a sliding door to a huge deck overlooking a level fenced backyard.  Hardwood floors and freshly painted throughout the main floor, the main bedroom is the entire finished upper level.  The main floor boasts a large bedroom and a second room that could be used as an additional bedroom or a den.  It has a door that leads to a breezeway between the den and attached oversized one car garage.  The garage has a second garage door to the backyard making it convenient to get a riding lawnmower or other equipment out with ease.  The basement is partially finished, just needs flooring.  It also has a shower, stool and sink near the laundry area.   This home is beautiful and waiting for it's new owner.
